OL,3,CTrump to hit 60 countries with fresh
OL,4,Ctariffs including new 10% UK levy
OL,6,FDonald Trump's government has
OL,7,Fannounced new double-digit tariffs on
OL,8,F60 countries, including the UK, after
OL,9,Ftime-limited levies introduced by the
OL,10,Fpresident following a Supreme Court
OL,11,Fdefeat expire on Friday.
OL,13,FThe US will impose tariffs of 10% to
OL,14,F12.5% on imports accounting for 99% of
OL,15,FUS imports, accusing countries of
OL,16,Ffailing to adequately enforce bans on
OL,17,Fgoods produced using forced labour.
OL,19,FThe UK will face a 10% import tariff
OL,20,Fon goods.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
