CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784845106
OL,3,CTrump to hit 60 countries with fresh
OL,4,Ctariffs including new 10% UK levy
OL,6,F"The United States has had a forced
OL,7,Flabour import ban for nearly a
OL,8,Fcentury, and rigorously enforces it;
OL,9,Fit's well past time for our trading
OL,10,Fpartners to do the same," US Trade
OL,11,FRepresentative Jamieson Greer said.
OL,13,F"Today's action will begin to correct
OL,14,Fwhat is both a human rights abuse and
OL,15,Fdistortive trade practice to improve
OL,16,Fthe welfare of workers everywhere."
OL,18,FThe new tariffs will take effect as
OL,19,Ftemporary 10% worldwide tariffs expire
OL,20,Fat 12.01am US local time on Friday.
