OL,3,CTrump to hit 60 countries with fresh
OL,4,Ctariffs including new 10% UK levy
OL,6,FTrump introduced the temporary levies
OL,7,Fafter the Supreme Court struck down
OL,8,Fhis biggest and most ambitious tariff
OL,9,Fmeasures in February.
OL,11,FNow he is turning to longer-lasting
OL,12,Ftariffs under Section 301 of the Trade
OL,13,FAct of 1974, which allows the
OL,14,Fpresident to impose import taxes and
OL,15,Fother sanctions on countries found to
OL,16,Fengage in "unjustifiable",
OL,17,F"unreasonable" or "discriminatory"
OL,18,Ftrade practices.
OL,26,@xD@KOUxD@YO]yD@AOUyD@NO]yD@SOUyD@bO]
