PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784845106
OL,3,CTrump to hit 60 countries with fresh
OL,4,Ctariffs including new 10% UK levy
OL,6,FThe president previously used Section
OL,7,F301 to impose major tariffs on China
OL,8,Fduring his first term, and those
OL,9,Fmeasures survived legal challenges.
OL,11,FMore Section 301 tariffs could be
OL,12,Fintroduced, with the US Trade
OL,13,FRepresentative's office investigating
OL,14,Fwhether 16 countries, accounting for
OL,15,F70% of US imports, have overproduced
OL,16,Fgoods, lowering prices and putting
OL,17,FAmerican companies at a disadvantage
OL,18,Fin global markets.
OL,20,FThe investigation has not yet been
OL,21,Fcompleted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
