OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784845106
OL,3,CTrump to hit 60 countries with fresh
OL,4,Ctariffs including new 10% UK levy
OL,6,FTrump, who argues that higher tariffs
OL,7,Fwill revive US manufacturing, last
OL,8,Fyear reversed decades of US policy
OL,9,Ffavouring lower tariffs and freer
OL,10,Ftrade.
OL,12,FUsing the 1977 International Emergency
OL,13,FEconomic Powers Act (IEEPA), he
OL,14,Fimposed double-digit tariffs on
OL,15,Fimports from almost every country,
OL,16,Farguing that America's long-standing
OL,17,Ftrade deficit represented a national
OL,18,Femergency.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
