OL,3,CTrump to hit 60 countries with fresh
OL,4,Ctariffs including new 10% UK levy
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FHowever, the Supreme Court ruled that
OL,12,FIEEPA did not give the president
OL,13,Fauthority to impose tariffs, forcing
OL,14,Fthe administration to issue refunds to
OL,15,Fimporters who had paid the charges.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
