OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784845106
OL,3,CTrump to hit 60 countries with fresh
OL,4,Ctariffs including new 10% UK levy
OL,6,FIn response, Trump introduced 10%
OL,7,Fworldwide tariffs under Section 122 of
OL,8,Fthe Trade Act of 1974. But those
OL,9,Ftariffs can only remain in place for
OL,10,F150 days, with the deadline expiring
OL,11,Fon Friday.
OL,13,FThe administration initially proposed
OL,14,Fthe forced labour tariffs last month.
OL,16,FSince then, some countries have
OL,17,Fstrengthened enforcement against
OL,18,Fforced labour and qualified for lower
OL,19,Ftariffs, according to a senior
OL,20,Fadministration official.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
